    {
      "sender_name": "2310tattoo studio by Christina",
      "timestamp_ms": 1771250058689,
      "content": "I\u00e2\u0080\u0099m writing this in translation so I don\u00e2\u0080\u0099t make any mistakes \u00f0\u009f\u0098\u0082\n\nGreat, now with the artists we have a better deal so they\u00e2\u0080\u0099re motivated to work. It\u00e2\u0080\u0099s not a fixed salary but a percentage, including on our studio\u00e2\u0080\u0099s tattoos.\nWe give 20% for our own clients. Usually we provide tattoos with a total daily value of \u00e2\u0082\u00ac350\u00e2\u0080\u0093\u00e2\u0082\u00ac450, so on average an artist makes \u00e2\u0082\u00ac70\u00e2\u0080\u0093\u00e2\u0082\u00ac90 per day for themselves from our ready clients.\n\nIf they manage to bring their own clients, the artist keeps 70% from their own client.\n\nTell me exactly which months you\u00e2\u0080\u0099re interested in coming so I can let you know if there will be work.\nFor March, April, and May we definitely have work and we can include you.\nAfter June, unfortunately we can\u00e2\u0080\u0099t guarantee that you will have work every day.",
